  stimulus_text = 'The author presents the idea that despite the technological advancement in the United States, the use of technology is not a panacea. "The problem is not a lack of technology. It''s that we’ve always had technology, but we’ve never been good at thinking about what it actually means to be human and how technology can serve those ends." The author believes that technology is merely a tool, and it is up to humans to decide how to use it.',
